      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 65.1 - 老子 65.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 65.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>古之善為道者，非以明民，將以愚之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The ancients who showed their skill in practising the Dao did so, not to enlighten the people, but rather to make them simple and ignorant.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-065__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-065</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 65.4 - 老子 65.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 65.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民之難治，以其智多。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The difficulty in governing the people arises from their having much knowledge.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-065__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-065</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
