      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 65.11 - 老子 65.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 65.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>常知稽式，是謂玄德。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ability to know this model and rule constitutes what we call the mysterious excellence (of a governor).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
