      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 65.13 - 老子 65.16</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 65.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>玄德深矣，遠矣，與物反矣，然後乃至大順。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Deep and far-reaching is such mysterious excellence, showing indeed its possessor as opposite to others, but leading them to a great conformity to him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
